</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64182865"><p>Those guys are arrogantly stupid. They think they can swindle people out of money so easily; I'm glad the FTC is still coming down on them hard.</p><p>They could've avoided that so easily, by doing any one of these variations:</p><p>"<i>File Now! Free for low-income individual and families</i>"<br>
